  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "PRODUCTION MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Conduct forecasting and planning of materials to ensure smooth production process.</li><li>Schedule and plan production activities based on job orders.</li><li>Monitor the lead time of producing the finished product.</li><li>Update and check inventory physical stock and arrange production of finished goods to meet the sales order.</li><li>Ensure production schedule meet the delivery date.</li><li>Liaise with suppliers for powder coating.</li><li>Troubleshoot discrepancies and quality issues.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Experience in aluminium working sector and manufacturing.</li><li>Able to lead team members on production and installation.</li><li>Have experience in working machineries.</li><li>Able to read technical and installation drawings.</li><li>Ensure products and install quality.</li><li>Planning of production schedules and allocate sufficient Manpower.</li><li>Implementation production processes and maximize efficiency and reduce production waste.</li><li>Implementing continuous process improvements.</li><li>Preparing material and equipment lists, PO, cost analyses and estimated cost.</li><li>Provide training staff for new production teams.</li></ul>",
